<exercise id="fs-idm216289408">
<problem id="fs-idm222487840">
<para id="fs-idm183058912"><link class="lo-reference" document="m68070"/>Stan is opening a coffee shop next to Big State University. He knows that controlling his costs will be important to the success of the shop. He will not be able to work all the hours the shop is open, so the employees will need some guidelines to perform their jobs correctly. After talking to an accounting professor, he decides he needs a standard cost system for his shop. Describe the process Stan should follow in setting his standards for materials and labor.</para>
